- Adds scripts/single_doorway.py (generate, continue, archive, open) preferring python3.12
- Adds wrappers: backlog_intake.py (advisory dedupe, Live Backlog only), prd_generator.py (Always-PRD, anchors, -vN on changes), task_generator.py (wraps generator; anchors; -vN on changes), executor.py (single active RUN with anchors; auto-resume; minimal state), archive_move.py (date-suffix runs; same-date -vN)
- Gates: ruff on touched files, linkage validator, help sanity

Gates to run:
- python3 scripts/single_doorway.py --help
- python3 scripts/validate_prd_backlog_linkage.py
- ruff check scripts/doorway_utils.py scripts/single_doorway.py scripts/backlog_intake.py scripts/prd_generator.py scripts/task_generator.py scripts/executor.py scripts/archive_move.py

Acceptance Criteria (B-108):
